description:
Onoya An is another transfer student at Aoba High School.
She`s actually http://anidb.net/ch81232 [Yoake Ryou]`s junior supervisor and the one who scouted http://anidb.net/ch79914 [Arata] for the experiment. Like Ryou, she acts cheerfully and together with watching their project to the point it becomes stalking, much to Arata`s annoyance.
Source: Wikipedia
name: Onoya An
